2079
01:34:38.214 --> 01:34:39.173
[Si-nae] Yah!

2080
01:34:41.342 --> 01:34:42.551
[gasps]

2081
01:34:42.635 --> 01:34:43.636
[A-ra gasps]

2082
01:34:44.512 --> 01:34:45.721
